      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, so there\u2019s not a scratch or a smudge in sight. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
