      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that redefines the 'used' category. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather still carries its original scent, with absolutely no bolster wear, creasing, or sun fading on the dashboard. Mechanically, it is flawless, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records organized in a comprehensive binder. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the moment it left the factory. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands perfection without compromise.",
